Program: Discovery
Title: Eathquakes - A warning for Istanbul
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz6z
Last Broadcast Date: 20 June 2006
The expectation that there will be a devastating earthquake in Istanbul, Turkey. Like many great cities Istanbul is built near a geological fault line. There has been a warning, though, the nearby earthquake in Izmit in 1999.